# Python Code Style

- Enforce PEP8 and keep max line length at `88`.
- Add type hints for all function parameters and return values.
- Add Google-style docstrings for all public methods/classes.
- Prefer clear names and small, single-purpose functions.
- Avoid hidden side effects and implicit global state.
